  "detailed_description": "Complete a mission, get info on your missing brother. That's the deal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find a way in</strong></h2>Were you able to find a key? Do you have a set of lock picks? Are you willing to break the lock and risk the repercussions?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cover your tracks</strong></h2>Put things back where they belong, close the cupboards, lock the door behind you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Don't get caught</strong></h2>Manage your anxiety, disable the alarm, dodge the security guard and get out before someone gets home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Complete the mission</strong></h2>Break into the computer, unlock the safe, do what you have to in order to get the item of interest, place the evidence or get the information needed to complete the mission.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Make the Call</strong></h2>Will you report them to the police? Expose them to the press? Help them? Hire them? Make a deal?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2>Improve your crafting tools, upgrade your lock picks, learn to stay calm under pressure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore</strong></h2>Maybe you'll find some interesting information to help you or others.",
  "about_the_game": "Complete a mission, get info on your missing brother. That's the deal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find a way in</strong></h2>Were you able to find a key? Do you have a set of lock picks? Are you willing to break the lock and risk the repercussions?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cover your tracks</strong></h2>Put things back where they belong, close the cupboards, lock the door behind you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Don't get caught</strong></h2>Manage your anxiety, disable the alarm, dodge the security guard and get out before someone gets home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Complete the mission</strong></h2>Break into the computer, unlock the safe, do what you have to in order to get the item of interest, place the evidence or get the information needed to complete the mission.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Make the Call</strong></h2>Will you report them to the police? Expose them to the press? Help them? Hire them? Make a deal?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2>Improve your crafting tools, upgrade your lock picks, learn to stay calm under pressure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore</strong></h2>Maybe you'll find some interesting information to help you or others.",
